{"tid":1460011,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"關於和理飛著唔著便服討論","createTime":"2019-08-13T00:39:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T01:29:18.000Z","uid":216268,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c7de1b13350f5379379e04747d63a6eb6610218a","tid":1460011,"uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:39:26.000Z","msg":"原來犬隻真係好驚我地著便服<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459702</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今曰見到尼個Po 有人話唔好著黑衫<br />\n不如大家討論下究竟著咩衫有咩好同壞<br />\n利申自己係著黑衫嘅 點解呢<br />\n原因有幾：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">易於識别</span></strong></span><br />\n無可否認 係現場一眼見到全黑陣型係好令人震奮 知道有同路人係身邊更加令人安心<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">表達意見</span></strong></span><br />\n黑衫由運動之初就已經代表緊我地一群人 唔單止代表我地嘅素求 更可以係媒體中一眼分辦出我地同其他群眾 有利於文宣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">既成習慣</span></strong></span><br />\n唔知大家對&ldquo;制服&rdquo;一詞點睇 中世紀民兵大多冇固定制服 記律鬆散 意志薄弱<br />\n原因好大係因為團隊凝聚力不足 而黑衫就好似屬於我地嘅&ldquo;制服&rdquo;咁 對我黎講佢提醒緊我地嘅訴求 都提醒我地要無忘初心<br />\n<br />\n好啦講左啲正方例子 我都講下我睇到嘅反方論點<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">唔易被人捉</span></strong></span><br />\n有指唔著黑衫唔易比人捉 捉到都可以扮遊客 可以冇事<br />\n<br />\n======================================<br />\n<br />\n尼個係我睇到嘅post(from the above link)<br />\n我個人覺得非法集結著咩衫固然可以做證 但我又真係唔覺得著便服有咩決定性嘅影響 同埋只要我地齊上齊落 不被捕嘅話 我唔明白點解要放棄黑衫<br />\n<br />\n其實講到底我覺得最重要嘅都係一大班人著黑衫係媒體報道時造成嘅<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">輿論效果</span></span></strong>影響最為重要 唔知大家點see<br />\n<br />\nanyway，開po嘅原因係想比大家討論下<br />\n以下開放討論"},{"pid":"5b73194be531dcf08d472f2ee9fde0cc76b283ba","tid":1460011,"uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:39:56.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"bcb75122daac81f9dc1f2a1514bfd32b804d7a9e","tid":1460011,"uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:40:06.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ac10a526998b7fa921a25cbe97567445e06c73f6","tid":1460011,"uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d714a2d5548c571157fc8ed73583c6e21612027","tid":1460011,"uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"316631ddcbc475035bdf351c1a5b1c2142c9dc35","tid":1460011,"uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6bf6e76a20cc64e746fe6d36b765e12570e1e52","tid":1460011,"uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f46abe5176e2e9586b241bc73d73a84e4f26b9","tid":1460011,"uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c672a8e4913eaa15a1ab5d325469dbcb205b1b4","tid":1460011,"uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:41:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db3b4c49f81a99b441d269023ff773f46b45cf2b","tid":1460011,"uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db35457189701ff4b858e3931f6e2940055934e8","tid":1460011,"uid":241224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:42:17.000Z","msg":"當刻可能唔會target到，但翻查cctv就好易認到"},{"pid":"c8a6d6b02721c03f508a2d95